									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
									</svg>
									Conexión USB-C única
