							</div>
							<div class="flex gap-3">
								<button onclick="addToCart('s900'); openCartModal();" class="flex-1 bg-accent text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-accent-hover transition-colors duration-300 font-medium text-center">
									Agregar al carrito
								</button>
								<a href="/extensor-2-monitores-s900" class="bg-gray-200 text-primary py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300 font-medium text-center">
									Ver más
								</a>
							</div>
						</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Producto 2: S788 - Extensor 3 Monitores -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden scroll-fade-in group">
					<a href="/extensor-3-monitores" class="block">
						<div class="relative overflow-hidden">
							<img 
								src="/S788/S788 mail pictures/S788主图 (1).jpg" 
								alt="Extensor Triple Screen S788" 
								class="w-full h-64 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
								loading="lazy"
							/>
							<div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-red-500 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
								Nuevo
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="p-6 md:p-8">
							<h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">
								Extensor Triple Screen S788
							</h3>
							<p class="text-secondary mb-4">
								El poder de 3 o 4 pantallas en un solo dispositivo portátil. Ideal para profesionales 
								que requieren múltiples espacios de trabajo simultáneos.
							</p>
							<ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
								<li class="flex items-center text-sm text-secondary">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
									</svg>
									3-4 pantallas desplegables portátiles
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-center text-sm text-secondary">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
									</svg>
									Resolución 1920×1200 por pantalla
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-center text-sm text-secondary">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
									</svg>
									Diseño plegable ultra portátil
								</li>
							</ul>
							<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
								<span class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent">Desde US$ 999</span>
								<a href="/extensor-3-monitores" class="text-accent font-medium group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
